====== inet-4.x ======

2017-09-12  Levente Mészáros

	All: Added alias for std::make_shared, std::dynamic_pointer_cast, etc. to
	support replacing the implementation.

	The reason to allow replacing the standard shared pointer is that it uses
	synchronization primitives to achieve thread safety. Thread safety is not
	required for INET simulations.

2017-09-11  Levente Mészáros

	All: Renamed byte -> B and bit -> b according to IEC & IEEE unit
	conventions.

2017-07-04  Levente Mészáros

	All: Added more const qualifiers to Ptr<> where possible.

2017-07-05  Levente Mészáros

	All: Followed recent const addition to Ptr<Chunk> in the Packet API.

2017-04-28  Zoltan Bojthe

	tcp: remove kludges

2017-04-25  Levente Mészáros

	Common: Renamed functions to include Be (Big Endian) in their names.

2017-04-11  Levente Mészáros

	All: Added type alias for std::shared_ptr called Ptr, this allows
	replacing the default implementation.

2017-04-11  Levente Mészáros

	Common: Completed MemoryInputStream implementation for bit streaming.

2017-04-11  Levente Mészáros

	Common: Completed MemoryOutputStream implementation for bit streaming.

2017-04-11  Levente Mészáros

	Common: Renamed to MemoryInputStream and MemoryOutputStream.

2017-03-09  Zoltan Bojthe

	TcpHeaderSerializer: kludge for fingerprint tests

2017-03-17  Levente Mészáros

	Common: Moved byte serialization loops into streams.

2017-03-02  Levente Mészáros

	Common: Renamed to ChunkSerializerRegistry.

2017-03-02  Levente Mészáros

	Common: Split Serializer.cc and Serializer.h according to classes.

2017-03-02  Levente Mészáros

	Common: Moved ChunkSerializer under common/packet/serializer.

2017-02-22  Levente Mészáros

	Serializer: Ported serialization of TCP options.

2017-02-21  Levente Mészáros

	Serialier: Dropped obsolete serializers.

2017-02-21  Levente Mészáros

	Serializer: Ported TcpHeaderSerializer partially.

2016-12-16  Levente Mészáros

	tcp

2017-01-25  Zoltan Bojthe

	TCPSegment renamed to TcpHeader

2016-10-17  Zoltan Bojthe

	tcpserializer fix

2016-10-14  Zoltan Bojthe

	tcp fixes

2016-10-14  Zoltan Bojthe

	FlatPacket: TCP uses it (lwIP, NSC is incomplete)
